[
    "User logged in",
    "Data processed"
] >> messages.

new FormatLog:
    @ >> msg.
    null >> Now >> ts.
    ts >> Str >> ts_str.
    (ts_str & " ") >> Split >> ts_parts.
    ts_parts[1] >> time_only.
    "[" >+> time_only >+> "] " >+> msg >> Return.
..

messages >~> FormatLog >> formatted.

"Formatted Logs:" >> Display.
formatted >!> @log:
    log >> Display.
..
